{"tid":33662,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"好憎啲教友","createTime":"2016-12-11T03:11:54.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T20:30:25.000Z","uid":51978,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e95cce671eab7e1307c299f4c7db1c43510baffd","tid":33662,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T03:11:54.000Z","msg":"有冇人覺得班教友簡直係低級趣味嘅極致？<br />\n填啲唔啱音嘅詞<br />\n以為好好笑<br />\n實則係以粗鄙無文為光榮<br />\n唔知醜<br />\n同班赤匪共狗嘅「無產階級文化」一樣<br />\n根本漢語(包括粵語)呢種聲調語言之中<br />\n填詞就係極考功夫嘅藝術<br />\n係文采嘅標誌<br />\n才華嘅象徵<br />\n經典之作足可傳世<br />\n代代詠唱<br />\n以前高登音樂台就出過無數雋永之歌<br />\n而家都買少見少<br />\n就係因為品味嘅墮落<br />\n<br />\n大家有冇同感？<br />\n<br />\n認真post"},{"pid":"ee1c3c650bd216df4c79dec6574154abf533ceae","tid":33662,"uid":6781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T04:16:24.000Z","msg":"主能夠 主撚尻"},{"pid":"c74bbdb196991718f4bc58aaa5f8de417b5dea69","tid":33662,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T04:19:39.000Z","msg":"填得岩音既改歌詞係好有趣，<br />\n不過班亂填又岸鳩當有趣既傻閪，真係嘔撚心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccd998e7651bac75c294f4c4e041beb544e8cdb6","tid":33662,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T22:44:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"684c325b572aff0e19e76f6e301dbb530602e78f","tid":33662,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T20:30:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}